Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Observation, hypothesis, experiment, and reflection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking scientifically...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the answer from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:31.52,white-large,,0,0,0,,{\pos(521.6,190.8)}Yu Aoi's\NThinking Practice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone did you think carefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,1. It will move away from our hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:45.67,black-small,,0,0,0,,{\pos(196,68.4)}Q. What will happen when a hand pulls the thread?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:45.67,black-small,,0,0,0,,{\pos(395.2,254)}3. It won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,2. It will move closer to the hand pulling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,3. It will turn in place without moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen?\NWatch carefully, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The spool moved towards the hand pullin the thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try that once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As we thought, it moved in the direction we're pulling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, let's try changing the size.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try this small spool of thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As we thought it moves twoards the hand pulling the thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As this is very curious,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone, please try it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But why should it do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the spool's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on we think for ourselves.
